data.description: An exceptional opportunity in Green Hill Farms. The approach has  a driveway or a curved front path leading to the sun porch. Upon entering through the arched front door the view of the spaces is exceptional. The living room boasts a wood-burning fireplace flanked by two built-in bookcases, while the dining room occupies the right side of the house. The main access hall is conveniently positioned next to the staircase. Adjacent to the hall and dining room,  is a quaint yet practical kitchen featuring a pantry closet, open shelves, modern appliances, and a pleasant view of the yard. Additionally, the main floor includes an attached garage, offering extra storage space. Upstairs, there are four bedrooms. The generously sized primary suite features an attached bathroom and a spacious closet. Accompanying the suite are three more bedrooms, complemented by a full hall bathroom. For added convenience, the bright finished basement provides extra living space, a full bathroom, and a laundry/utility room, enhancing the array of amenities this property has to offer. Beyond the interior, a very nice concrete patio seamlessly connects to the driveway and looks out to the backyard.
